82
00:05:41,560 --> 00:05:43,680
I hold your hand, through life we'll go.

83
00:05:43,680 --> 00:05:45,720
Long live the Emperor!

84
00:05:46,080 --> 00:05:48,480
(This should all have been mine.)

85
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:52,520
