the long parting is hard to bear♪

108
00:09:03,730 --> 00:09:08,150
♪Life and death, a tale in the play♪

109
00:09:08,350 --> 00:09:10,890
♪Memories grow cold♪

110
00:09:10,890 --> 00:09:17,720
