to the heartless?♪

111
00:09:17,870 --> 00:09:22,140
♪Our happy life is but a dream♪

112
00:09:22,460 --> 00:09:24,990
♪We'll wake up eventually♪

113
00:09:24,990 --> 00:09:31,970
