130
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,520
Yes.

131
00:10:38,180 --> 00:10:42,120
Chuxi, treasure this destined bond well.

132
00:10:42,360 --> 00:10:43,200
Yes.

133
00:10:45,480 --> 00:10:47,760
Let's toast to this.

134
00:10:47,760 --> 00:10:48,720
- Come on.
- Come on.

135
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,200
- Cheers.
- Cheers.

